The paper discusses the use of cooperative adaptive cruise control (CACC) systems in connected and automated vehicles, which involves aspects of control systems (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), cybernetics (cs.CY), and information theory (cs.IT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
